We kill him. I can cut his brakes.

44
00:02:10.255 --> 00:02:12.674
-My cousin's a mechanic. He showed me how. -No. no. no. no. no.

45
00:02:12.757 --> 00:02:14.801
No. If anything. we'd make it look like an overdose.

46
00:02:14.884 --> 00:02:16.511
-But we're not doing that!

47
00:02:16.594 --> 00:02:18.346
Well. we have to do something.

48
00:02:18.429 --> 00:02:21.474
Look. my job is as good as gone if Cam takes over. He hates my ass.

49
