One time. I caught him using my eye shadow. and he never forgave me.

50
00:02:24.644 --> 00:02:26.229
Look. if you wanna put a stop to this.

51
00:02:26.312 --> 00:02:28.439
you have to convince Stephen not to sell his shares.

52
00:02:28.523 --> 00:02:30.150
-Yes! Stephen! -Right.

53
00:02:30.775 --> 00:02:31.776
Okay. I'm gonna find him.

54
00:02:31.860 --> 00:02:33.945
And we always have the overdose option as a backup.

55
00:02:34.028 --> 00:02:37.240
Ali. there can be no evidence that we ever spoke of that.

56
00:02:37.740 --> 00:02:39.534
-Just act casual.

57
00:02:42.537 --> 00:02:45.290
- Hey. she's not in her office. - I know.

58
