I don't like this. I don't like this at all.

59
00:02:47.333 --> 00:02:48.334
I'm getting itchy.

60
00:02:48.418 --> 00:02:50.670
-Are my hives resurfacing? -Oh God!

61
00:02:50.753 --> 00:02:52.088
How are they pulsating?

62
00:02:52.172 --> 00:02:54.174
