63
00:02:54.257 --> 00:02:57.218
Why can't we figure out a way that Isla and Cam both get what they want?

64
00:02:57.302 --> 00:03:00.054
Like if I gave you $20 and you put calamine lotion on my back.

65
00:03:00.138 --> 00:03:02.515
Stop. Stop. Maybe we can fix this. you know?

66
00:03:02.599 --> 00:03:04.934
There's… there's a lot of power being in the middle.

67
00:03:05.018 --> 00:03:07.979
Yeah. we play it like CT and Trishelle on Traitors season 2.

68
00:03:08.062 --> 00:03:10.690
You watch Traitors? Why didn't you tell me? We could…

69
00:03:10.773 --> 00:03:12.400
Never mind. Let's go talk to Cam.

70
00:03:12.483 --> 00:03:14.485
