71
00:03:14.569 --> 00:03:15.403
-Okay. -Okay.

72
00:03:15.486 --> 00:03:18.114
Hey. would you want to do a Traitors podcast with me?

73
00:03:18.198 --> 00:03:21.951
-We call it Alan Cummings and Goings. -I'm not doing another podcast with you.

74
00:03:22.035 --> 00:03:22.869
♪ Movin' up. up ♪

75
