81
00:03:38.426 --> 00:03:39.552
Oh. wow.

82
00:03:39.636 --> 00:03:42.096
Well. I'll just come visit you after the season.

83
00:03:42.180 --> 00:03:43.890
Actually. I used to play in Sofia

84
