It's a lot of work with Austin. and he's a method actor.

87
00:03:58.071 --> 00:03:58.905
Wait a minute.

88
00:03:59.489 --> 00:04:02.992
Are you breaking up with me so you can pretend to be Austin Butler's wife?

89
