115
00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:12.437
Isla. I like you. and I do respect what you've done.

116
00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:15.106
but I can't turn down the kinda money that Al is offering.

117
00:05:15.189 --> 00:05:18.151
