118
00:05:18.234 --> 00:05:21.154
Not unless you find someone that'll pay me more money than Al.

119
00:05:21.654 --> 00:05:23.865
Okay. Well. then that's what I'm gonna do.

120
00:05:23.948 --> 00:05:26.617
