140
00:06:13.915 --> 00:06:17.001
but Ness and I are the highest level employees here.

141
00:06:17.085 --> 00:06:19.462
and we've worked with both you and Isla.

142
00:06:19.545 --> 00:06:25.009
Yeah. and… and in transition times like this. we could be very crucial.

143
