154
00:06:55.081 --> 00:06:56.457
-Yeah. -Yeah.

155
00:06:57.125 --> 00:06:58.960
Okay. Bring it in.

156
00:06:59.043 --> 00:06:59.919
Come on!

157
00:07:01.796 --> 00:07:03.256
You're my baby bro. I love you.

158
00:07:04.215 --> 00:07:05.800
