-Isla. no. You… Give me that. -Ew.

238
00:10:40.598 --> 00:10:42.099
Hey. yo. Dyson. Hold up. man.

239
00:10:42.183 --> 00:10:44.644
Don't worry about tonight. bro. We'll get 'em back game two.

240
00:10:44.727 --> 00:10:48.022
Man. I don't even care. The news just came out about Zoé's movie.

